          <div class="post-date">Dec 6, 2024</div>
          <h2 class="post-title">Why I'm Starting This</h2>
          <div class="post-content">
            <p>I've spent 14 years building products, writing code, and solving problems. But I've rarely documented the journey - the messy middle, the small wins, the questions that keep me up at night.</p>
            <p>This space is for the unscripted parts. The real work behind the LinkedIn highlights. The learning that happens between meetings. The thoughts that don't fit in a user story.</p>
            <p>I'm here to show up, write honestly, and track my purpose, progress, and presence - one day at a time.</p>
