          <div class="post-date">Dec 5, 2024</div>
          <h2 class="post-title">Between Meetings and Meaning</h2>
          <div class="post-content">
            <p>Today was back-to-back meetings. Sprint planning, system reviews, stakeholder updates. Somewhere between the third and fourth call, I realized I was operating on autopilot.</p>
            <p>It's easy to confuse being busy with making progress. The real question isn't "what did I do today?" but "did I move closer to what matters?"</p>
            <p>Tomorrow I'm blocking 30 minutes just to think. No agenda. Just space.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="post-tags">
            <span class="tag">Work</span>
            <span class="tag">Reflection</span>
            <span class="tag">Presence</span>
